          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>People Empowerment Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the government of Guam to obtain voter approval through a referendum for an issuance of municipal bonds in an amount greater than $25 million, an increase in a tax, or the imposition of a new tax. </p>]]></text>
